name: Fuck La Rat Race (Limited Sketch Edition)
description:
French sketch rap, where I express my feelings about the rat race.

I'm a web developer who wants to explore new domains (covid realization), like music and writing.
I make sketchs with my computer, to train/explore my own vision of hip hop (in french, english or guadeloupean kréyòl). And I wanted to mint NFT on Hic&Nunc.

You can listen it for free. And if you liked the song, you can support my art by buying this NFT.

I will surely plan free content, in the future, for every owner of my music NFTs. 

That's what NFT's about, isn't it ?!
